  <description type="morphology">Plants annual, glabrous; taproot 2–10 cm. Stems prostrate, succulent; trichomes at
        nodes and in inflorescence absent or inconspicuous; branches to 56 cm. Leaf blades obovate
        or spatulate, flattened, 4–28 × 2–13 mm, apex round to retuse or nearly truncate;
        involucrelike leaves 1–4. Flowers 3–10 mm diam.; petals yellow, oblong, 3–4.6 × 1.8–3 mm;
        stamens 6–12(–20); stigmas 3–6. Capsules ovoid, 4–9 mm diam. Seeds black or dark brown,
        orbiculate or elongate, flattened, 0.6–1.1 mm; surface cells ± smooth, granular, or
        stellate, with rounded tubercles. 2n = 18, 36, 54.</description>
